"You just installed the Odoo for Hotel package. By doing so, we have "
"installed a\n"
"            bunch of necessary apps to run your Hotel efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Vous venez d’installer le pack Odoo pour Hôtel. Celui-ci inclut un ensemble "
"d’applications essentielles pour gérer votre établissement efficacement."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You may be running multiple places at the same time and most likely be "
"willing to run them all from the same database.<b/>We got you covered with "
"this using multiple companies or branches!"
msgstr ""
"Vous gérez peut-être plusieurs sites en même temps et souhaitez très "
